1. *Zadatak* je da završim svoju domaću zadaću do kraja nedelje. (The task is to finish my homework by the end of the week.)

2. On je preuzeo *zadatak* da sastavi plan. (He took on the task to compose a plan.)

3. Svi smo mi odgovorni za izvršenje *zadatka*. (We are all responsible for the completion of the task.)

4. Ona je završila svoj *zadatak* pre roka. (She completed her task ahead of time.)

5. *Zadatak* nam je da razrešimo problem. (Our task is to solve the problem.)